mdElement.text: localhost
Method get is default.

Files posted to localhost will be located within service context (that means in the /bin directory of the running service (e.g. <projecthome>\bin\urlUrl.UrlAdapterExample. UrlAdapterExample\bin).

.\tmp\ refers to this context and posts the file to the tmp directory of the service.

The directory where the file should be created is defined in the  component diagram on the alias postFile).

In this case the file new_address.xml should be created at "localhost", meaning the machine which this repository is deployed to.
NOTE: Generally, to handle files on file-systems we recommend to use the <<FileSystemAdapter>> instead of the <<URLAdapter>>.
